## Proposed Solution

### Fix 1: ESC Key Double-Fire (CRITICAL)
**Root Cause:** Need to investigate why both handlers fire despite priority system.

**Approach:**
1. Add console logging to useEscapeKey to track event flow
2. Check if Modal's onClose is triggering a re-render that registers a second listener
3. Add early return if event was already processed (`e.defaultPrevented`)

**Proposed Fix:**
```typescript
// src/hooks/useEscapeKey.ts line 27
const handleEscape = (e: KeyboardEvent) => {
  if (e.key === 'Escape') {
    // Early return if already processed
    if (e.defaultPrevented) return;

    const currentPriority = (e as any)._escPriority || -1;

    if (priority > currentPriority) {
      (e as any)._escPriority = priority;
      e.stopPropagation();
      e.preventDefault(); // This marks event as processed
      onEscape();
    }
  }
};
```

**Time Estimate:** 30 minutes (investigation + fix)

### Fix 2: Notes Placeholder Positioning (CRITICAL)
**Root Cause:** Absolute positioning places it in formatting bar, not editor content.

**Approach:** Use Lexical's native placeholder positioning (which positions relative to first editor line).

**Proposed Fix:**
```typescript
// src/widgets/NotesEditor.tsx line 732
placeholder={
  <div className="editor-placeholder text-text-light-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary pointer-events-none opacity-60">
    Start writing...
  </div>
}
```

Remove `absolute top-3 left-3` positioning entirely. Lexical handles placeholder positioning internally.

**Time Estimate:** 15 minutes

### Fix 3: Footer Visibility (HIGH)
**Root Cause:** Full-width footer (`left-0 right-0`) goes under sidebar.

**Approach:** Revert to original bottom-right positioning OR use margin-left to account for sidebar.

**Proposed Fix (Option 1 - Revert to Original):**
```typescript
// src/components/Footer.tsx
return (
  <>
    {/* Footer - Bottom with centered content */}
    <motion.footer
      initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 50 }}
      animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
      transition={{ duration: 0.3, ease: [0.4, 0, 0.2, 1] }}
      className="fixed bottom-4 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-30 pointer-events-none"
    >
      <div className="flex items-center gap-6 px-6 py-3 bg-white/90 dark:bg-surface-dark/90 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-full border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark pointer-events-auto shadow-lg">
        {/* Links */}
        <button onClick={() => setShowAboutModal(true)}>About Us</button>
        <span>|</span>
        <button onClick={() => navigate('/privacy')}>Privacy Policy</button>
        <span>|</span>
        <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Neuman Brain</span>

        {/* Save Status */}
        <div className="flex items-center gap-2 ml-6">
          <span className="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full ..."></span>
          <span>{getStatusText()}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </motion.footer>

    {/* About Modal */}
    {showAboutModal && <AboutModal onClose={() => setShowAboutModal(false)} />}
  </>
);
```

This centers the footer as a floating pill at bottom-center, visible regardless of sidebar state.

**Time Estimate:** 30 minutes

